Chat for Support Supervisors (Salesforce Classic)

Welcome to Chat! With supervisor tools, you can monitor agents' activities, assist them in chats, and view chat session data. This applies only to Chat in Salesforce Classic.

Available in: Salesforce Classic
Available in: Performance Editions and Developer Edition orgs created after June 14, 2012
Available in: Unlimited Edition and Enterprise Edition with Service Cloud

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED:
To chat with visitors in the console: Chat is enabled, set up, and included in a console app

The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026.

As a support supervisor, oversee employees to provide best customer support. Chat is fully integrated with Salesforce, making it easy to access information about agents and their chat activity.
